Complete Acne Regimen


The Effaclar Acne System contains a unique set of dermatological ingredients to provide fast, gentle, and visible results with continuous improvement, week after week.
 DISCOVER THE EFFACLAR SYSTEM 








Up to 60% Reduction of Acne In 10 Days


See for yourself why thousands of dermatologists use Effaclar to treat patients’ acne. See visible results starting day 1 and continuously week after week.
SEE MORE BEFORE / AFTER RESULTS








Watch Testimonials



Watch dermatologists and patients share their Effaclar story and learn about their transformational results.
 WATCH WHAT REAL USERS ARE SAYING 


















How It Works
Effaclar Medicated Gel Cleanser thoroughly cleanses, removes excess oil and impurities. [2.0%] Salicylic Acid Acne Medication fights acne breakouts. [0.05%] Exclusive micro-exfoliating Lipo Hydroxy Acid helps target oily areas on the skin surface to gently provide precise cell-by-cell removal of debris and dirt.




How To Use
Cleanse with Effaclar Medicated Gel
Use 2x daily, morning and evening, using fingertips in a gentle rotating motion on wet face. Rinse thoroughly.









How It Works
Effaclar Clarifying solution gently tones while clearing clogged pores and exfoliating. [2.0%] Glycolic Acid penetrates deep to unclog pores and smooth skin texture. [0.5%] Salicylic Acid Acne Medication helps to reduce any remaining mild imperfections.




How To Use
Apply Effaclar Clarifying Toner
Tone up to 2x daily after cleansing, using a soft cotton ball or pad on dry face. No rinsing necessary. Avoid entire eye area.









How It Works
Effaclar Duo Dual action treatment is clinically proven to fight acne and clear even stubborn blemishes, blackheads and whiteheads. [5.5%] Micronized Benzoyl Peroxide Acne Medication penetrates deep into skin to fight all types of acne blemishes. [0.4%] Exclusive Micro-Exfoliating Lipo Hydroxy Acid provides precise cell-by-cell exfoliation to smooth skin texture.




How To Use
Finish with Effaclar DUO
Treat up to 3x daily morning and/or evening on affected areas with a thin layer.












Real 10-Day Photos. Un-Retouched. No Face Make-Up.





REDUCES UP TO 60% OF ACNE IN 10 DAYS
See for yourself why thousands of dermatologists use Effaclar to treat their patients’ acne. This unique and innovative 3-step system is the only system with dermatologist-recommended Effaclar Duo acne treatment that reduces up to 60% of acne in just 10 days. Now see visible results starting day 1 and continuously week after week with the new Effaclar Dermatological Acne System.




ABRA M. | 10-DAY RESULTS
"With Effaclar I have continuous improvement. I have less redness and less red bumps. It’s incredible because I feel like Effaclar was made for somebody like me. And that feels really good."



CYNTHIA M. | 10-DAY RESULTS
“Within 10 days, Effaclar cleared up my skin. And no new breakouts from the time I started. Just continuously got better.”



HAYLEE S. | 10-DAY RESULTS
"After 10 days, I feel my skin for the first time in years is smooth. Seeing the positive change going on, I know my skin will only continue to heal."



REBEKAH G. | 10-DAY RESULTS
"After 10 days, my acne has improved dramatically and I don't feel terrified to go in public without makeup. No more bumps!"









Testimonials




NO HARSH SCRUBS, DERMATOLOGIST RECOMMENDED
The secret to fighting acne is not to use harsh scrubs as they can potentially damage and irritate acne-prone skin, making it more sensitive.


More Testimonials



Watch Video
DERMATOLOGIST'S REVIEWS
Learn why dermatologists trust and recommend La Roche-Posay’s Effaclar to treat acne. By using a combination of active ingredients and no harsh scrubs, Effaclar provides fast, gentle, visible results in just 10 days.



 Watch Video
FAST AND CONTINUOUS RESULTS
See up to 60% reduction of acne in just 10 days with continuous results week after week.

 Watch Video
GENTLE EVEN ON SENSITIVE SKIN
Treating acne should not aggravate the skin, that’s what Effaclar is formulated and tested to be suitable for even sensitive skin.

 Watch Video
NO HARSH SCRUBS, DERMATOLOGIST RECOMMENDED
The secret to fighting acne is not to use harsh scrubs as they can potentially damage and irritate acne-prone skin, making it more sensitive.

 Watch Video
EFFECTIVE ON ADULT ACNE
Treating adult acne is a unique approach that requires sophisticated formulas with elegant textures that maximize compliance for better results.









Working With Dermatologists




Developing skin care products alongside dermatologists is a critical part of the La Roche-Posay mission to transform your quality of life.








#BeClearBootcamp

Get more expert advice about acne on the #BeClearBootcamp. We partnered with dermatologists to provide you with condensed content to get you all the facts you need to know about acne.
