About La Roche-Posay



La Roche-Posay treatments consist of two fundamental principles: high standards and dermatological safety. La Roche-Posay products contain thermal spring water combined with a minimum, but optimum, concentration of selective ingredients. Our Anthelios and Effaclar line is extremely popular for suncare and acne treatment. The formulas are developed such that their concentration of ingredients within their skin care products are very gentle on the skin, while remaining totally effective. The tests developed by La Roche-Posay Pharmaceutical Laboratory are among the cosmetics industry's most demanding in order to ensure optimum safety. Each product must demonstrate its effectiveness according to strict criteria; namely, a visible result, confirmed by a dermatologist, and effectiveness that is scientifically measured against a placebo or a reference product.






























